        {
            "title": "摩根士丹利:這支七巨頭股票是「財報前戰術性做好」的好選擇",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/AByqyNzxprCWO5C_D9FUWg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPED9U0NH_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 蘋果(Apple)是「財報前戰術性做好」的標的,<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"摩根士丹利\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:摩根士丹利;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/摩根士丹利\">摩根士丹利</a>分析師Erik Woodring表示,他認為這家iPhone製造商即將公佈的業績將是一個結算事件,為該股接下來季節性強勢的時期鋪路。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Woodring預期第一季(3月季度)營收和每股盈餘將較市場共識預期溫和上揚1%至2%,但供應限制將限制進一步的漲幅。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">對於第二季(6月季度),摩根士丹利的營收預測較市場預期高出5%,但毛利率預測較市場共識低170個點子,得出的每股盈餘預測為1.74美元,與市場預期一致。該行認為這一結果好於市場擔憂的情況。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-8a9f3e5a-7c66-3d6b-865a-fa67d6227c3a-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">記憶體成本上升預計將對毛利率構成壓力,但摩根士丹利表示,iPhone、Mac和服務營收的持續強勁應能抵消這一不利因素。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">除了近期財報外,該行認為有幾個催化劑將支撐該股至年底,包括供應鏈調查顯示市場份額增長、蘋果將於6月8日舉行的全球開發者大會(市場預期較低,但Siri的重大重新設計可能成為情緒面的順風)、以及秋季推出可摺疊iPhone。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">摩根士丹利還指出,在大型科技股同業資本支出上升的背景下,蘋果的自由現金流產生能力是相對的正面因素。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該行對<span><span><span><span>蘋果</span></span></span></span>給予增持評級,目標價為315美元,基於2027財年每股盈餘9.76美元,較市場共識高出約5%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Woodring寫道:「我們認為蘋果股價有望在今年9月達到300美元,受溫和的本益比擴張和更強勁的正面每股盈餘上修所推動。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%91%A9%E6%A0%B9%E5%A3%AB%E4%B8%B9%E5%88%A9-%E9%80%99%E6%94%AF%E4%B8%83%E5%B7%A8%E9%A0%AD%E8%82%A1%E7%A5%A8%E6%98%AF-%E8%B2%A1%E5%A0%B1%E5%89%8D%E6%88%B0%E8%A1%93%E6%80%A7%E5%81%9A%E5%A5%BD-%E7%9A%84%E5%A5%BD%E9%81%B8%E6%93%87-124033127.html",
