        {
            "title": "國泰世華攜Visa推CUBE App小額跨境匯款 支援八國幣別最快30分鐘到帳",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"214\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/OkBBXqTE9vZM1Fm0HVorrw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTcwNTtoPTM5Nw--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/cnyes_hk_559/7d3f6a4324f6f97f0c1b411b13eec880\" width=\"380\"/></div></figure></div>",
